as part of the `assets` query parameter. 

A `PriceHistory` object will include the asset name and a list of 
`(timestamp, price)` tuples representing historical price snapshots:

```json
{
    "asset": "dai",
    "prices": [
      [1581724800, "0.0035"],
      [1581811200, "0.0038"]
      ...
    ]
